-- Monte dei Paschi readies senior unsecured bond issue - source
-- 
-- Mon Mar 24, 2014 10:15AM EDT
-- None



MILAN, March 24 (Reuters) - Italy's thid-biggest bank by branches Monte dei Paschi di Siena <BMPS.MI> is preparing to launch a senior unsecured bond with a benchmark size of around 500 million euros ($689.12 million), a source with direct knowledge of the deal told Reuters on Monday.

